Artichokes are amongst us! Stuffedartichokes: part 2

Stuffed artichokes are popping up everywhere and I’m not looking for them! But I now was determined to remove my stuffed artichoke from my car since I got a new home that was just perfect for it!!

The Moran family tomb houses a famous restauranteur “Diamond Jim” who did stuff his meatballs (probably also his artichokes )!

He stuffed his meatballs with diamond rings for the pretty ladies! His restaurant was very popular, and the Moran family still runs it on Bourbon St!

They definitely had a Sicilian menu and stuffed artichokes are a must in local Sicilian cuisine!

Now  I put pennies , nickels, dimes and coins of the real in mine but mine  are Voodoo offerings;what are diamonds? Mob related?!

He was best friends with Lucky Luciano, so I am not stereotyping here people! But them again, if I could, I would put diamond rings In my artichokes too!
